title: HOUR 1- Oct 02, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Oct 02, 2020
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan and Co. discuss the fast-paced action of MLB's Wild Card round, as well as who Dan really wants in the World Series. Also, Brooklyn Nets guard Kyrie Irving made several comments on a podcast recently and the show reacts.
